LVDS-1#1 Warning
Bidirection LVDS IOs  
The following port(s) use the LVDS_25 I/O standard and have bi-directional differential usage. Please note that LVDS_25 is a fixed impedance structure optimized to 100ohm differential. This is only intended to be used in point-to-point transmissions that do not have turn around timing requirements. If the intended usage is a bus structure, please use BLVDS/BLVDS_25, instead. ext_clk_i_n, ext_clk_i_p, lvds_n_i, lvds_p_i, valid_n_i, valid_p_i.
